    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, my dad just got in from his flight from tokyo. he’s saying his left arm feels kind of heavy and tingly, and he sounds a bit weird when he talks, like his speech is thick or something. he thinks he might just be exhausted from the long trip though. is that normal after a long flight?",
