      "content": "wait really? i don't know... he’s also been complaining about some weird pressure in his chest and a headache since he landed. he's acting pretty calm about it though, just says he needs to lie down and sleep it off. you sure it can't just be extreme exhaustion or dehydration from the cabin air? he's an older guy so i don't want to cause a huge scene if it's nothing.",
